		<npcWinRock_1>Rock beats scissors! I win!</npcWinRock_1>
		<npcWinRock_2>I win! The rock beats scissors!</npcWinRock_2>
		<npcWinRock_3>I win this round!</npcWinRock_3>
		<npcLosePaper_1>Scissors cut paper! You win!</npcLosePaper_1>
		<npcLosePaper_2>Your scissors win this round!</npcLosePaper_2>
		<npcLosePaper_3>You chose scissors! You win!</npcLosePaper_3>
